finish

public abstract void finish()
                     throws java.rmi.RemoteException
Description copied from interface: INode
Removes this node from registry handler and destroys it.
Results of trying to use this node after calling this method are unpredictable.
This method may result in a RemoteException if it was not possible to notify the registry or the main node (in the case of a process node).

addNodeEventListener

public void addNodeEventListener(INodeEventListener listener)
                          throws java.rmi.RemoteException
Description copied from interface: INode
Adds a node event listener to this node. IMPORTANT: You can only add event listeners on a node started in the same JVM. Trying to add listeners on a remote node will result in a "RemoteException" beeing thrown.
